w:r.w:t: A Shopify apps called “VKS Shipping Rates” to allow a Shopify Admin user to create different shipping rate as at the Home->
pps area after login to Shopify Admin backend.
Each Shipping Rate will include the following fields
Zone Name: Contain of maximum 30-50 characters
and regions: a dropdown menu containing a list of countries in which each country provides a list of regions in dropdown menu format for the user to click to choose
District: the user can input a list of district name which can be separated by a “comma”. E.g. Wong Tai Sin, Tin Hau, Wan Chai
Purchase Threshold amount: it is a numeric value
Shipping fee: the default fee to charge the customer when the purchase threshold amount criteria is met
Enable or Disable flag: A dropdown list for the user to set it Active when “Enable” flag is chosen and vice versa
can be created by the Shopify Admin whenever there is a need.
The first phase of the VKS Shipping Rates apps is designed for Hong Kong only. Hong Kong has 3 regions, namely:
And there are 18 districts among these 3 regions. There is no postcode in Hong Kong
After the user login to Shopify backend, the VKS Shipping Rate apps can be access as follows:
The admin user can click “Add shipping zone” icon to create new shipping fee
Input user interface to create new shipping zone, part 1
Input detail of a new shipping zone, part 2
and regions from a dropdown menu where a list of country with the regions associated with that country can be clicked to select.
